OL,3,CPolice still looking for answers 22
OL,4,Cyears after hospital carer shot and
OL,5,Ckilled
OL,7,FPolice are urging anyone with answers
OL,8,Fto come forward nearly 22 years after
OL,9,Fa young hospital carer died after
OL,10,Fbeing shot.
OL,12,FCraig Eaton was just 22 when he was
OL,13,Fshot dead on Molyneux Road in
OL,14,FKensington, Liverpool, shortly after
OL,15,F11.15pm on 24 February 2004.
OL,17,FMore than two decades later, the
OL,18,Ffamily of the carer who worked at
OL,19,FAlder Hey Children's Hospital, say
OL,20,Fthey are still waiting for justice.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/7
