OL,3,CPolice still looking for answers 22
OL,4,Cyears after hospital carer shot and
OL,5,Ckilled
OL,7,FOn the day Craig was killed Merseyside
OL,8,FPolice believe he boarded the number
OL,9,F26 Arriva bus on Belmont Road,
OL,10,Ftravelling to Sheil Road, where he got
OL,11,Foff between 11.05pm and 11.15pm.
OL,13,FMinutes later, as he walked along
OL,14,FMolyneux Road near the junction with
OL,15,FMallow Road, he was shot.
OL,17,FDespite the efforts of a passerby, he
OL,18,Fdied at Royal Liverpool University
OL,19,FHospital.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/7
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
