CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F398A1771883475
OL,3,CPolice still looking for answers 22
OL,4,Cyears after hospital carer shot and
OL,5,Ckilled
OL,7,FDetectives say they believe Craig was
OL,8,Fnot the intended target - and are
OL,9,Furging those who live locally and have
OL,10,Fremained silent despite knowing what
OL,11,Fmay have happened to come forward.
OL,13,FIn the 22 years since the shooting,
OL,14,Fofficers have traced bus passengers,
OL,15,Fexamined CCTV and tracked the
OL,16,Fmovements of two cars believed to have
OL,17,Fbeen in the area that night, including
OL,18,Fa stolen dark green Ford Mondeo and a
OL,19,Fsilver-blue Volvo 740 GL.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/7
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
