OL,3,CPolice still looking for answers 22
OL,4,Cyears after hospital carer shot and
OL,5,Ckilled
OL,7,FOn the night he was killed, Craig had
OL,8,Fbeen mourning the loss of two-year-old
OL,9,FMichael Tierney, a boy he had helped
OL,10,Fcare for and had grown close to during
OL,11,Fhis time at the hospital.
OL,13,FThe toddler was left blind with
OL,14,Fcerebral palsy and epilepsy after
OL,15,Fbeing starved of oxygen during his
OL,16,Fbirth which left him needing round-the-
OL,17,Fclock care.
OL,19,FWhen the toddler died, Craig had spent
OL,20,Fthe evening with a friend before
OL,21,Fsetting off alone.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/7
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
