OL,3,CPolice still looking for answers 22
OL,4,Cyears after hospital carer shot and
OL,5,Ckilled
OL,7,FHoward Rubbery, Head of the Serious
OL,8,FCrime Review Unit at Merseyside
OL,9,FPolice, said: "Craig's family are
OL,10,Fstill searching for answers 22 years
OL,11,Fafter his murder and we are committed
OL,12,Fto get justice for them.
OL,14,F"We know that somewhere in Liverpool,
OL,15,Fsomebody knows who killed Craig which
OL,16,Fis why our investigation remains open
OL,17,Fand is regularly reviewed.
OL,26,@vD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/7
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
