OL,3,CPolice still looking for answers 22
OL,4,Cyears after hospital carer shot and
OL,5,Ckilled
OL,7,F"Although 22 years have passed since
OL,8,FCraig's death, there is no time limit
OL,9,Fon providing information. We know
OL,10,Fthere are people who were out that
OL,11,Fnight on Tuesday 24 February when
OL,12,FCraig was murdered and know who was
OL,13,Fresponsible.
OL,15,F"If you are one of those people please
OL,16,Fcome forward and tell us what you
OL,17,Fknow. Your circumstances may have
OL,18,Fchanged and you may feel brave enough
OL,19,Fto come forward and do the right
OL,20,Fthing."
OL,26,@oD@AOUwD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/7
